,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c8280e2f08af366878510376eae26e5ea0791059","tid":2478022,"uid":80162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T18:40:22.000Z","msg":"介紹下graphql有咩好壞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T18:55:50.000Z","msg":"簡單黎講就係將個N+1 problem由frontend推左去backend<br />\ngraphql最重要係define左query個shape，可以explicitly決定返黎嘅data有咩fields<br />\n去到backend，最極限可以根據你嘅query去generate SQL query去join曬exactly你要嘅資料，一次DB query就搞掂。但就算多左fields，只要你無query到都唔會return返去frontend<br />\n而且因爲全部野都係explicitly typed，配合埋graphql-code-generator可以做到完美frontend-server-db typesafe，即係全部都有auto complete<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}